Package: gp3sequences
Title: Transparent Analysis of Ordered Categorical Sequences
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person(
      given = "Stefanos",
      family = "Balaskas",
      email = "s.balaskas@ac.upatras.gr",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2444-9796")
    )
Description: Provides transparent, reproducible, and auditable tools for validating,
    preparing, encoding, summarising, comparing, and modelling ordered
    categorical sequence data. Supports explicit preprocessing policies,
    contiguous motifs, aligned-position consensus, descriptive group
    comparisons, edit and transition distances, clustering diagnostics,
    transition networks, categorical hidden Markov models, and guarded
    adapters to specialist sequence-analysis packages.
